<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَيُسْتَخْدَمُ في عِلاَجِ الحُمَّى<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>قَالَ لَكِنْ تَعِيبُهُ مَرَارَة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَمَا حَمِدْتُ مَرَّةً آثَارَه<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>قَالَ نَعَمْ مُرٌّ وَهَذَا عَيْبُهُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مُذْ كُنْتُ يَا مَوْلاَيَ لاَ أُحِبُّهُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>هَذَا الَّذِي مَاتَ بِهِ بُقْرَاطُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَحَذَّرَ أَيْضَاً مِنهُ سُقْرَاطُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَالْتَفَتَ السُّلْطَانُ لِمَن حَوْلَهُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَقَالَ كَيْفَ تجِدُونَ قَوْلَهُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>قَالَ الْوَزِيرُ يَا سَيِّدَ النَّاسِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>دَعْ كَذِبي وَخُذْ مِنيِّ إِينَاسِي<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>جُعِلْتُ كَيْ أُنَادِمَ السُّلْطَانَا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>لاَ لِكَيْ أُنَادِمَ الْبَاذِنجَانَا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c3">{أَمِيرُ الشُّعَرَاء / أَحْمَد شَوْقِي بِتَصَرُّف}</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>الشَّيْطَانُ في ثَوْبِ الزَّاهِدِين<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>حِكَايَةُ الصَّيَّادِ وَالْعُصْفُورَة<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>صَارَتْ لِبَعْضِ الزَّاهِدِينَ صُورَة<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>مَا هَزِءتُ فِيهَا بِمُسْتَحِقِّ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَلاَ أَرَدْتُ أَوْلِيَاءَ الحَقِّ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>مَا كُلُّ أَهْلِ الزُّهْدِ صَادِقِينَا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>كَمْ بَينَ أَهْلِ الزُّهْدِ فَاسِقِينَا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>